# meet mode - Google Meet controls
## d: toggle mic (sends Cmd+D to Chrome/browser)
meet < d : osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to keystroke "d" using command down'

## e: toggle camera (sends Cmd+E)
meet < e : osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to keystroke "e" using command down'

## q: leave call (sends Cmd+Shift+B for "leave")
meet < q : osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to keystroke "b" using {command down, shift down}'

# quick meet shortcuts (no mode required)
## hyper + d: quick mic toggle
cmd + shift + alt + ctrl - d : osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to keystroke "d" using command down'

# quick ghostty - cmd+shift+return to open new ghostty window
cmd + shift - return : ~/bin/ghostty-create-window

# toggle keybind cheatsheet popup
ctrl - 0x2C : sketchybar --set mode popup.drawing=toggle
